T1  - Interest rates and monetary policy uncertainty
AU  - Stulz, RenéM.
JO  - Journal of Monetary Economics
VL  - 17
IS  - 3
SP  - 331
EP  - 347
PY  - 1986
DA  - 1986/05/01/
